<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-496] Quickstart scripts go out of date</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-496</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The various quickstart instructions and scripts go out of date quickly. Approaching the Mahout project as a beginner is often frustrating.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I suggest that quickstart scripts should be part of the build and tested regularly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
