                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12982434" author="srowen" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2011 00:08:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Auto-testing would be nice though I imagine a fair bit trickier than a unit test. Are there specific problems that can be solved here? The quickest way to make a case that something needs to be done is to highlight the current issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12982441" author="tdunning" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2011 00:36:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Presumably, the testing wouldn&apos;t need to be quite as thorough as a unit test.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A concrete example of a regression along these lines is how the ModelDissector seems to have started putting out different numbers when fed an SGD model.  I would have preferred that this had been found immediately by a test rather than a user.  I am fixing the problem and will try to put in a test, but the point remains.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12982457" author="tdunning" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2011 03:00:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is an extension to the TrainLogisticTest that tests that two examples stay working.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12982458" author="tdunning" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2011 03:01:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am committing that patch since it should be non-controversial.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12982503" author="hudson" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2011 07:04:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Mahout-Quality #563 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Mahout-Quality/563/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Mahout-Quality/563/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-496&quot; title=&quot;Quickstart scripts go out of date&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-496&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-496&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; - Fixed &quot;simplification&quot; of string constant.  There is no change so small it cannot be screwed up.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13037254" author="srowen" created="Sat, 21 May 2011 04:13:57 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This is mostly subsumed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-707&quot; title=&quot;Setup Jenkins Jobs to validate our Examples/bin Scripts&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-707&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-707&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and partly resolved it seems anyway.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
